---
title: Beef Koftas & Veggie Brown Rice with Garlic-Cucumber Raita
description: These koftas are handy parcels of flavour, with tender mince, mild spices and a smattering of almonds to add extra texture.
Paired with a veggie-packed brown rice and tangy yoghurt, this is a Middle Eastern feast to remember.
